221
00:08:27,120 --> 00:08:29,160
the echoes of the Scriptures

222
00:08:29,160 --> 00:08:31,880
that you, I hope, will discern through it

223
00:08:31,880 --> 00:08:32,240
It says

224
00:08:32,240 --> 00:08:33,600
We are committed to world mission

225
00:08:33,600 --> 00:08:34,720
because it is central

226
00:08:34,720 --> 00:08:36,320
to our understanding of God

227
00:08:36,320 --> 00:08:38,880
the Bible, the Church, human history

228
00:08:38,880 --> 00:08:40,480
and the ultimate future

229
00:08:40,480 --> 00:08:41,600
The whole Bible

230
00:08:41,600 --> 00:08:43,400
reveals the mission of God

231
00:08:43,400 --> 00:08:45,920
to bring all things in heaven and on earth

232
00:08:45,920 --> 00:08:48,000
into unity under Christ

233
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:49,160
reconciling them through

234
00:08:49,160 --> 00:08:50,720
the blood of His cross

235
00:08:50,720 --> 00:08:52,080
There's Colossians

236
00:08:52,080 --> 00:08:53,640
In fulfilling His mission

237
00:08:53,640 --> 00:08:55,640
God will transform the creation

238
00:08:55,640 --> 00:08:57,440
broken by sin and evil

239
00:08:57,440 --> 00:08:58,800
into the new creation

240
00:08:58,800 --> 00:09:00,200
in which there is no more

241
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:02,200
sin or curse

