244
00:09:06,480 --> 00:09:07,880
through the gospel of Jesus

245
00:09:07,880 --> 00:09:10,800
the Messiah, the seed of Abraham

246
00:09:10,800 --> 00:09:12,360
God will transform

247
00:09:12,360 --> 00:09:14,560
this fractured world of nations

248
00:09:14,560 --> 00:09:16,960
that are scattered under the judgment of God

249
00:09:16,960 --> 00:09:18,360
into the new humanity

250
00:09:18,360 --> 00:09:20,760
that will be redeemed by the blood of Christ

251
00:09:20,760 --> 00:09:23,880
from every tribe, nation, tongue and language

252
00:09:23,880 --> 00:09:25,280
