God will destroy the reign of death

255
00:09:29,320 --> 00:09:31,120
corruption and violence

256
00:09:31,120 --> 00:09:32,960
when Christ returns to establish

257
00:09:32,960 --> 00:09:35,360
His eternal reign of life

