278
00:10:17,080 --> 00:10:18,280
from its beginning

279
00:10:18,280 --> 00:10:20,480
promise right through to its conclusion

280
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:23,000
But within that story

281
00:10:23,000 --> 00:10:25,160
or that drama of the scripture

282
00:10:25,160 --> 00:10:28,920
God has chosen to have a partner

283
