00:11:06,560 --> 00:11:08,960
and then to go on serving

300
00:11:08,960 --> 00:11:11,400
worshipping and glorifying God

301
00:11:11,400 --> 00:11:12,840
for all eternity

302
00:11:12,840 --> 00:11:13,760
in the world to come

