00:12:41,640 --> 00:12:43,480
very quickly read them

344
00:12:43,480 --> 00:12:45,360
The Lord said to Abram

345
00:12:45,360 --> 00:12:47,240
Go from your country, your people

346
00:12:47,240 --> 00:12:48,400
and your father's household

347
00:12:48,400 --> 00:12:50,240
to the land that I will show you

348
00:12:50,240 --> 00:12:52,240
I will make you into a great nation

349
00:12:52,240 --> 00:12:53,840
and I will bless you

350
00:12:53,840 --> 00:12:55,320
I will make your name great

351
00:12:55,320 --> 00:12:56,840
and be a blessing

352
00:12:56,840 --> 00:12:58,800
or you will be a blessing

353
00:12:58,800 --> 00:13:00,480
I will bless those who curse you

354
00:13:00,480 --> 00:13:02,280
and whoever who bless you

355
00:13:02,280 --> 00:13:05,280
I will bless those who bless you

356
00:13:05,280 --> 00:13:07,520
and whoever curses you I will curse

357
00:13:07,520 --> 00:13:09,320
and bottom line

358
00:13:09,320 --> 00:13:11,240
all peoples on earth

359
00:13:11,240 --> 00:13:13,640
will be blessed through you

360
00:13:13,640 --> 00:13:15,200
Now it's not hard to hear

361
00:13:15,200 --> 00:13:17,040
what the key word in those verses are

362
00:13:17,040 --> 00:13:18,520
It's the word bless and blessing

363
00:13:18,520 --> 00:13:20,600
which shines through about five times

364
00:13:20,600 --> 00:13:21,880
in three verses

365
00:13:21,880 --> 00:13:23,320
And this is very good news

366
00:13:23,320 --> 00:13:25,920
because this is Genesis 12

367
00:13:25,920 --> 00:13:28,800
which comes after Genesis 11

368
00:13:28,800 --> 00:13:30,240
You need to know these things

369
00:13:30,240 --> 00:13:32,480
You don't get a PhD for nothing

370
00:13:32,480 --> 00:13:34,480
But it's not just the arithmetic

371
00:13:34,480 --> 00:13:36,760
because as I was saying this morning

372
00:13:36,760 --> 00:13:38,960
Genesis 11 is the sort of climax

373
00:13:38,960 --> 00:13:40,840
of the story of human fallenness

374
00:13:40,840 --> 00:13:42,360
and sin and rebellion

375
00:13:42,360 --> 00:13:43,360
coming to its climax

376
00:13:43,360 --> 00:13:44,600
in the Tower of Babel

377
00:13:44,600 --> 00:13:46,520
and the scattering of the nations

378
00:13:46,520 --> 00:13:49,200
Genesis 12 suddenly is good news

379
00:13:49,200 --> 00:13:50,440
all over again

380
00:13:50,440 --> 00:13:51,920
that God is going to bring blessing

381
00:13:51,920 --> 00:13:53,200
into the world

382
00:13:53,200 --> 00:13:54,320
So it's no wonder therefore

383
00:13:54,320 --> 00:13:56,960
the Apostle Paul quotes this text

384
00:13:56,960 --> 00:13:58,480
as what he calls

385
00:13:58,480 --> 00:14:00,480
in Galatians 3 verses 8 and 9

386
00:14:00,480 --> 00:14:02,480
the gospel in advance

387
00:14:02,480 --> 00:14:03,520
That's what he said

388
00:14:03,520 --> 00:14:04,520
that the scriptures

389
00:14:04,520 --> 00:14:06,240
preach the gospel in advance

390
00:14:06,240 --> 00:14:07,880
So Abraham saying

391
00:14:07,880 --> 00:14:10,080
through you all nations will be blessed

392
00:14:10,080 --> 00:14:11,440
The Greek literally is

393
00:14:11,440 --> 00:14:14,040
he pre-evangelized Abraham

394
00:14:14,040 --> 00:14:15,800
Here's God's great surprise

395
00:14:15,800 --> 00:14:16,800
good news

396
00:14:16,800 --> 00:14:18,480
that in spite of all that has happened

397
00:14:18,480 --> 00:14:20,480
in chapters 4, 3 to 11

398
00:14:20,480 --> 00:14:22,080
God still intends

399
00:14:22,080 --> 00:14:24,440
to bless the nations of the earth

400
00:14:24,440 --> 00:14:26,160
And he would launch this mission

401
00:14:26,160 --> 00:14:28,160
through Abraham and his people

402
00:14:28,160 --> 00:14:30,880
So therefore as we were thinking earlier

403
00:14:30,880 --> 00:14:33,920
there is a universal purpose

404
00:14:33,920 --> 00:14:36,560
to the existence of particular Israel

405
00:14:36,560 --> 00:14:38,480
Israel as a nation exists

406
00:14:38,480 --> 00:14:41,360
for the sake of God's ultimate purpose

407
00:14:41,360 --> 00:14:43,400
for the whole of humanity

408
00:14:43,400 --> 00:14:47,120
And this fundamentally missional intention

409
00:14:47,120 --> 00:14:48,840
of the election of Israel

410
00:14:48,840 --> 00:14:50,080
echoes on and on

411
00:14:50,080 --> 00:14:51,800
through the Old Testament

412
00:14:51,800 --> 00:14:53,840
Now you kindly referred to my book

413
00:14:53,840 --> 00:14:54,640
The Mission of God

414
00:14:54,640 --> 00:14:56,040
And there's a whole chapter on this

