00:15:45,320 --> 00:15:46,360
Mind you sometimes I wonder

443
00:15:46,360 --> 00:15:47,720
what's going through the mind of Christians

444
00:15:47,720 --> 00:15:49,760
when they sing our hymns and songs as well

